▸ I N I C I O — C Ó M O E J E C U T A R
Arch Linux / Konsole
chmod +x spydragon.sh
./spydragon.sh
Kali / Parrot / Ubuntu
chmod +x spydragon.sh
bash spydragon.sh
Instalar dependencias (Arch)
sudo pacman -S curl nmap whois bind-too
ls traceroute openssl python
Instalar dependencias (Debian/Ubuntu)
sudo apt install curl nmap whois dnsuti
ls traceroute openssl python3
